This repository is provided as a research/reproducibility and portfolio package
for the MICCAI 2017 White Matter Hyperintensities (WMH) Segmentation Challenge
(Kuijf et al., IEEE TMI 2019). The pipeline is inherited from the sibling repo
isles2022-2d3d-blend-reproducible-pipeline; see docs/inheritance/inheritance_map.md
for the exact mapping of code reused vs. WMH-specific additions.

It is NOT a medical device and is NOT intended for clinical decision making.

No datasets, trained weights, runs, results, or logs are included in this
repository. Users must obtain the MICCAI 2017 WMH Segmentation Challenge data
separately from https://wmh.isi.uu.nl/ and comply with the applicable data use
agreement.

